<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>来自江门龙口镇的牛肉，新鲜！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还有牛沙腩吃，你吃过吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 🍌香蕉仔×牛头角·龙口牛肉料理福利🐂 </strong></p>
